    %% Required Dependencies
    Feast -->|container orchestration| K8s
    Feast -->|runtime| Python
    Feast -->|HTTP API framework| FastAPI
    Feast -->|ASGI server| Uvicorn
    Feast -->|WSGI server| Gunicorn
    Feast -->|data serialization| Protobuf
    Feast -->|data manipulation| Pandas
    Feast -->|columnar data| PyArrow
    Feast -->|database abstraction| SQLAlchemy

    %% Optional Storage
    Feast -.->|online store| Redis
    Feast -.->|online/offline store| PostgreSQL
    Feast -.->|offline store| BigQuery
    Feast -.->|online/offline store| Snowflake
    Feast -.->|online store| DynamoDB
    Feast -.->|registry backend| S3
    Feast -.->|registry backend| GCS
    Feast -.->|online store| MongoDB
    Feast -.->|online store| Cassandra
    Feast -.->|online store| ClickHouse

    %% Internal ODH
    Feast -.->|mTLS & authorization| Istio
    Feast -.->|external access| Route
    Feast -->|metrics| Prometheus
    Feast -.->|TLS certificates| CertManager

    %% ML Platform
    Feast -->|feature selection| MLflow
    Feast -->|pipeline integration| Kubeflow
    KServe -->|feature retrieval| Feast
    Seldon -->|feature retrieval| Feast

    %% Data Processing
    Feast -.->|batch engineering| Spark
    Feast -.->|distributed batch| Dask
    Feast -.->|distributed batch| Ray
    Feast -.->|streaming ingestion| Kafka

    %% Observability
    Feast -.->|distributed tracing| OpenTelemetry
    Feast -.->|data lineage| OpenLineage

